    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Add:</p>\n\n<pre><code>build.gradle \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>in your root project folder, and use plugin for example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>apply plugin: 'idea'\n//and standard one\napply plugin: 'java'\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and with this fire from command line:</p>\n\n<pre><code>gradle cleanIdea \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and after that:</p>\n\n<pre><code>gradle idea\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>After that everything should work </p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 392860,
