    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There is no need to remove any <code>.iml</code> files. Follow this:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>close the project</li>\n<li><code>File</code> <code>-&gt;</code> <code>Open...</code> and choose your newly created <code>build.gradle</code></li>\n<li>IntelliJ will ask you whether you want:\n\n<ul>\n<li><code>Open Existing Project</code></li>\n<li><strong><code>Delete Existing Project and Import</code></strong></li>\n</ul></li>\n<li>Choose the second option and you are done</li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
