    "answer_id" : 46233362,
    "question_id" : 26745541,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In IntelliJ 2017.2.4 I just closed the project and reopened it and I got a dialog asking me if I wanted to link with <em>build.gradle</em> which opened up the import dialog for Gradle projects.</p>\n\n<p>No need to delete any files or add the <em>idea</em> plugin to <em>build.gradle</em>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4483663,
      "reputation" : 14163,
      "user_id" : 3647002,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 47,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/WR7iJ.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Gayan Weerakutti",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3647002/gayan-weerakutti"
